import { Typography } from '@mui/material'
import { Box } from '@mui/system'
import React from 'react'

const Contact = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Box className='hero_section' height={"100vh"} flexDirection={"column"}>
                <Typography variant='h2' sx={{ textAlign: 'center', fontSize: '140px', fontWeight: '500', color: "#111", mb: "2rem" }}>
                    Lets Connect
                </Typography>
                <button className='btn_underline'>
                    <Typography variant='h5' sx={{ textAlign: 'center', fontSize: '14px', fontWeight: '500', color: "#111" }}>
                        Contact Us
                    </Typography>
                </button>
            </Box>

        </>
    )
}

export default Contact
